00:19:37,169 --> 00:19:41,371
I'm ensuring that the right
person is held responsible.

532
00:19:41,439 --> 00:19:44,547
Look, come on, I've been helpful
before, haven't I, Detective?

533
00:19:44,548 --> 00:19:46,276
You step out of line one time...

534
00:19:46,344 --> 00:19:47,978
You can give me a right-good
spanking, I promise.

535
00:19:48,045 --> 00:19:50,447
Come on, let's go.

536
00:19:50,514 --> 00:19:52,648
MAN: Ty wouldn't do something like this.

537
00:19:52,716 --> 00:19:53,916
He's such a good kid.

538
00:19:53,985 --> 00:19:55,750
I'm actually more curious
about you, Mr. Hanson.

539
00:19:55,818 --> 00:19:56,852
Me? (chuckles)

540
00:19:56,919 --> 00:19:58,354
Why? I didn't even go to the party.

541
00:19:58,421 --> 00:19:59,754
I had to work.

542
00:19:59,822 --> 00:20:01,923
CHLOE: You spoke to the victim a
few hours before she was killed.

543
00:20:01,992 --> 00:20:05,727
Maybe it's best if I don't say
anything without my attorney.

544
00:20:05,795 --> 00:20:07,496
Joey! Joe, Joe.

545
00:20:07,563 --> 00:20:08,864
There's no need for that.

546
00:20:08,931 --> 00:20:10,799
Why don't you

547
00:20:10,867 --> 00:20:12,867
